            <li><strong>Multiple game modes:</strong> cube, ship, ball, UFO, wave, robot, and more.</li>
            <li><strong>Icon customization:</strong> unlock new shapes, colors, and trails as you progress.</li>
            <li><strong>Practice mode:</strong> place checkpoints and train difficult sections safely.</li>
