          <p>Many players prefer to play Geometry Dash on PC because a keyboard or gamepad often feels more precise than a touchscreen. On desktop you can also enjoy a larger screen, which makes it easier to read the level and react to obstacles in time.</p>
          
          <hr/>
          
          <h2>Geometry Dash levels</h2>
          
          <h3>A wide variety to explore</h3>
          <p>Geometry Dash offers a wide range of levels with different speeds, visual themes, and difficulty. Early levels introduce basic jumps and short sections, while later levels mix gravity changes, portals, and fast sequences that test everything you have learned.</p>
          
