          <hr/>
          
          <h2>Game modes in Geometry Dash</h2>
          <p>Geometry Dash is not just a simple cube that jumps. As you play, portals transform your character into different forms with unique physics. For example, the ship lets you fly up and down, the ball switches gravity with every tap, and the wave moves in a zig-zag line that demands very precise control.</p>
          
          <p>Learning how each mode behaves is crucial. The same tap that makes the cube hop over a spike will make the wave shoot up sharply. Before trying to beat a hard level, spend time in practice mode learning how each form reacts to your inputs.</p>
          
