          <hr/>
          
          <h2>FAQ</h2>
          
          <h3>Is Geometry Dash free to play on geometrydash.ie?</h3>
          <p>Yes. The browser version on geometrydash.ie is free to play. You do not need to register or install anything.</p>
          
          <h3>Can I play Geometry Dash on mobile and PC?</h3>
